high_descs: Turn around to reach the sofa.
Pick up the yellow mango from the couch.
Turn right to head down the passage and reach the fridge on the left.
Put the yellow mango in the fridge to cool and take it out.
Turn around to reach the dining table.
Put the yellow mango on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled Mango on the DiningTable.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sofa behind you.
Pick up the mango on the couch.
Turn right and then take a left into the kitchen and go to the fridge.
Put the mango in the refrigerator and take it back out.
Turn around and go to the dining table behind you.
Put the mango on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Place a mango on a dining room table.

high_descs: Exit from the room, turn right, go straight, turn left, again turn right to the sofa.
Pick up the mango from the sofa.
turn around go straight and turn left to reach the fridge.
Open the cupboard, put the mango on the table, close the cupboard, wait for 5 minutes, then open the cupboard again.
Take the fruit from the diningtable and turn around.
Keep the mango along with put on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Keep the mango along with put on the dining table.
